net.bytebuddy.description.field

接口 FieldList<T extends FieldDescription>

  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of field descriptions represented by this list.
    所有超级接口:
    Collection<T>, FilterableList<T,FieldList<T>>, Iterable<T>, List<T>
    所有已知实现类:
    FieldList.AbstractBase, FieldList.Empty, FieldList.Explicit, FieldList.ForLoadedFields, FieldList.ForTokens, FieldList.TypeSubstituting, TypePool.Default.LazyTypeDescription.FieldTokenList

    public interface FieldList<T extends FieldDescription>
extends FilterableList<T,FieldList<T>>
    Implementations represent a list of field descriptions.

      An implementation of a field list for an array of loaded fields.

      A list of field descriptions for a list of detached tokens.

      • asTokenList

        ByteCodeElement.Token.TokenList<FieldDescription.Token> asTokenList(ElementMatcher<? super TypeDescription> matcher)
        Transforms the list of field descriptions into a list of detached tokens. All types that are matched by the provided target type matcher are substituted by TargetType.
        参数:
        matcher - A matcher that indicates type substitution.
        返回:
        The transformed token list.

      • asDefined

        FieldList<FieldDescription.InDefinedShape> asDefined()
        Returns this list of these field descriptions resolved to their defined shape.
        返回:
        A list of fields in their defined shape.
